"{\"uid\": \"katherinetimes.com.au-story-8707084-katherine-celebrates-church-milestone-and-olympic-streaming\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Elected Members will have a stall at the market on the 3rd of August from 9.00am - 12.00pm.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 91, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a chance for our community to come and have a look at the plans for the Pool, get a copy of the Municipal Plan, the Council Community Grants Program and any other information about council that you would like.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  Activate Katherine is hoping to Live Stream the Olympics in the town square for the duration.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine\", \"score\": 0.9372194189282359, \"rank\": 0.06698193161123543, \"text\": \"Katherine\", \"types\": [\"Q82799\", \"Q202444\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katherine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be more information as the time draws near.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope everyone enjoyed the Show.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Congratulations to all the winners of all the entries.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joanna Holden was presented with the Katherine Town Council Volunteer of the Show trophy.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanna_of_Castile\", \"score\": 0.9330279882252428, \"rank\": 0.07093517162525076, \"text\": \"Joanna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanna_of_Castile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joanna_of_Castile\"}, {\"begin\": 593, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.